                        <interp inst="t18391021-name-1259" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE BURGESS</persName>
                  </hi>. Mrs. Bailey gave me these things on the 3rd of August.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18391021-name-1260" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18391021-name-1260" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18391021-name-1260" type="surname" value="BAILEY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18391021-name-1260" type="given" value="ELIZABETH"></interp>ELIZABETH BAILEY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the wife of Thomas Bailey, who is a private in the Marines at Woolwich. The prisoner lodged with me, she made me a present of these things, and when she left me I missed a ring.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> Did not Mrs. Bertram say she gave me a piece of stuff? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes, but not these.</p>
